text: ITC Officina Sans ITC Officina Sans Italic ITC Officina Serif ITC Officina Serif Italic Beeline ITC Officina is a font superfamily designed by Erik Spiekermann and released in 1990. It consists of ITC Officina Sans, ITC Officina Serif and ITC Officina Display, with bold, italic, and small-caps variations of each. == Sources == * Typedia == External links == * Official website Officina Officina Officina Officina
